<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200809/e02657d8c4614956bd2c09fd007f2531.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">杨家川小峡谷的河湾与游船。</span></img></p>
